CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1962, pg. 5 reads: "Two Years Old - Sylvia Ann Porter celebrated her second birthday recently at a party at the home of her parents. The pretty little miss is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Fred Pryor Jr. of Homewood. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Fred Pryor Jr., standing with boys and girls, gathered around Sylvia Ann Porter wearing plaid pinafore dress, for second birthday party, Homewood
